{"tid":843128,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳費Sir憂曼聯成英超笑柄","createTime":"2018-10-01T02:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T04:09:40.000Z","uid":147522,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25aae76a8415672c8dcf6da7ab55dcca0851e3c9","tid":843128,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrIngEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=c47adaad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】自領隊費格遜離開之後，英超豪門曼聯中興無期，更有傳爵爺非常擔心，怕曼聯將長久失去光芒。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯傳奇領隊費格遜（Sir Alex Ferguson）帶領「紅魔鬼」奪得13次英超冠軍，與曼聯情誼之深毋寧置疑。看到球會近年成績下滑，多次易帥仍未見起色，有傳費格遜與友人表示非常擔心，懼怕曼聯淪為「馬戲團球會」，成英超笑柄。<br />\n<br />\n除了爵爺之外，近日不少曼聯名宿表達不安，「92班」主將加利尼維利認為球會一開始就已經「自毀長城」，沒有給予一眾領隊充裕時間組軍，而里奧費迪南就表示：「單單球會的事並非事情之全部，場內場外大小事情都是足球的一部分。現時的曼聯並未表現出成功球會的運作風格，尤其是你要保持球隊內的團結一致。」"},{"pid":"89576f0c4cf0ff4392adccde4a273c51376e52f9","tid":843128,"uid":10503,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:41:57.000Z","msg":"而家已經係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd99f69df8ff8592f08ca4ceeab82474c2aa6ec","tid":843128,"uid":6577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89576f0c4cf0ff4392adccde4a273c51376e52f9","tid":843128,"uid":10503,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:41:57.000Z","msg":"而家已經係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3